    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs((0.69 - (v2 + 0.30 - tmp + 0.98)))
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.17) / v0) * tmp)
    v0 = (0.46 / wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.05)))
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.80) + 0.61) - wp.abs((v2 + 0.41 * v0 + 0.60)))
